name: "Sigh" Cake - Dragon fruit
description: @Sugartivi | Dear art collector, sometimes the best way to deal when things are not going our way - is to really feel the disappointment. This is hard but it lets us move onward. This Sigh cake is made with dragon fruit: Dragon fruit always looks crazy, bright and wild, but the actual flavor when you bite it is surprisingly gentle and mild. Things are often not what they seem.
